          sampleAnswer: '**PESTLE (Vietnam)**: P: Government encourages e-commerce E: GDP growth 6% + growing middle class S: Young population/high mobile penetration T: Mobile payment widespread L: Foreign investment restrictions require JV E: Weak logistics infrastructure\n**Five Forces**: Intense existing competition (Shopee burning cash) + price-sensitive buyers + low entry barriers but scale is a moat\n**SWOT**: S: Tech capability + warehouse experience W: Don\'t understand Vietnam market + no local team O: Market growth + niche categories T: Shopee scale + local e-commerce\n**Recommendation**: Conditional Go -- enter via niche categories (beauty/food from Taiwan) + find local partner, don\'t compete head-to-head with Shopee\n**BMC**: Customer: 25-35 women VP: Authentic Taiwan products + fast shipping Channel: Social + KOL Revenue: Products + commission',
